  <brief_title>Evaluation of the Physiopathological Phenomena and the Haemodynamic and Cerebral Metabolic Effects From Semi-seated Position to Lying Position in Patients With Brain Trauma</brief_title>
  <acronym>PULSATILITY</acronym>
